Description: Composable neural-network operations on top of the anvl
    XLA array-computing package: broadcast-aware helpers, softmax,
    layer and RMS normalization, SiLU, scaled dot-product attention,
    rotary position embeddings, and linear layers, plus safetensors
    weight loading with float32 upcast. The forge accessory for the
    anvil.
